{"tid":1592294,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"曼聯創紀錄 活華特：全力支持蘇B","createTime":"2019-09-24T14:09:32.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-24T14:10:58.000Z","uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"0e9767a928ddc8848e9a43a73781c30aada0d8be","tid":1592294,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T14:09:32.000Z","msg":"【Now Sports-體育】曼聯CEO活華特周二宣佈年度財務報告，球會收入達到6.27億鎊，再創歷史新高。<br />\n<br />\n即使近年曼聯成績未如理想，球會在財政收入卻不斷創下新高。周二曼聯CEO活華特（Ed Woodward）宣佈年度財務報告，曼聯收入達到6.27億鎊，利潤為5000萬鎊。<br />\n<br />\n活華特指出：「我們仍然按照球會與領隊的理念，專注於重建計劃與加強青訓系統。最近我們新簽下3名優秀的一隊成員，和關鍵球員續約，青訓球員亦展現了天份。曼聯的每位成員都努力以贏得冠軍為首要目標。」言下之意，即使剛剛曼聯於英超又輸一場，跌至積分榜第8位，球會對領隊蘇斯克查是百份百支持。<br />\n<br />\n另外，因為曼聯缺席了今季的歐聯賽事，2020財年總收入預計會下降至5.6至5.8億鎊。<br />\n<br />\n圖片來源 : &copy;AFP"},{"pid":"02ba4a0a7ffce4a31eb06267e6c633172021a96c","tid":1592294,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T14:09:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/biFbOWs.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbiFbOWs.png&h=404dfcfc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n【929行動】大家好，我地係Chinazi。<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1590320\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1590320</a>"},{"pid":"a3aca0db45027d0c4cfd89a21d8b75c250c1ed7c","tid":1592294,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T14:10:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/09/23/155817_9438652f50d82865bf1f7dadaa552e9d.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F09%2F23%2F155817_9438652f50d82865bf1f7dadaa552e9d.png&h=3585e476&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n個個一鳩樣 廢事再炒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}